thread.title: Rosemary

author: Rosemary
title: Rosemary
text:
I highly recommend Francesca Gulluni as a Property Manager with Nelson Alexander who is managing my property at 9 Smith St. Francesca, has provided me with helpful advice and has always followed up and carried out any enquiries I have made. All communications have been prompt and efficient. I was impressed with Francesca's professionalism and friendliness; she is helpful, making me feel relaxed and confident in her abilities. Within one week of listing my property on the rental market she found a fantastic tenant, who met my requirements. It is reassuring to know that my rental property, which is a new apartment, is now being managed and cared for with the same level of pride which I would give.
Francesca, thank you for all your efforts and communications in managing my property and finding the right tenant for my property.
Regards Rosemary Sarr
